---
// src/components/shared/Footer.astro
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-zinc-900 text-zinc-300 py-16 border-t border-zinc-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 block">
          <span class="text-primary">psycho</span>logic.
        </a>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-light max-w-sm mb-8 leading-relaxed">Un espacio seguro y confidencial para tu salud mental. Terapia online basada en evidencia clínica.</p>
        
        <!-- Emergency -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-2xl p-5 border border-zinc-700/50 max-w-md shadow-inner">
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-300 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
            Atención en Crisis / Emergencias
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed">Si estás pasando por una crisis severa o tienes pensamientos suicidas, no estás solo. Comunícate a la línea de prevención (Ej. <span class="text-white font-medium">*4141 en Chile</span>) o asiste a urgencias de inmediato.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-6 tracking-wide">Navegación</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-light text-zinc-400">
          <li><a href="#sobre-mi" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Sobre Mí</a></li>
          <li><a href="#especialidades" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Especialidades</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Preguntas Frecuentes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#agendar" class="text-primary hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium">Agendar Hora</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Contact -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-6 tracking-wide">Contacto</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-light text-zinc-400">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg> contacto@psychologic.com</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg> +56 9 1234 5678</li>
          <li class="pt-4 flex gap-5">
            <a href="#" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-primary transition-colors">Instagram</a>
            <a href="#" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-primary transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-zinc-800/80 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm font-light text-zinc-500">
      <p>&copy; {year} psycho-logic. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Términos de Servicio</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Políticas de Privacidad</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
